<br>
if you dont want to cheat, then mez the bonedancer.  you should be able to one shot a healer pet with added DDs.  might need to give it a tap with a fast 1h weapon first.  if you can kill a healer pet in the first 3 seconds after you mez the bonedancer, then you can easily kill the second pet before mez breaks.  then mez the commander and pray for no crits on the instant lifetaps.<br>
<br>
if you're playing on a server where mid has power relics dont plan on winning very much, that pushes the lifetaps to an obscene level.<br>
